item.title: CVE-2022-3679|2024-08-03T01:14:03.236Z -- unknown -- starter%20templates%20by%20kadence%20wp
item.description: The Starter Templates by Kadence WP WordPress plugin before 1.2.17 unserialises the content of an imported file, which could lead to PHP object injection issues when an admin import (intentionally or not) a malicious file and a suitable gadget chain is present on the blog.
